item.title: About Me
item.description: I'm Rakan Al Masri, third semester CS student at the Karlsruhe Institute of Technology (KIT). My interests include Personal Finance, Gaming, Mathematics, Languages and Programming. I love immersing myself in new cultures,which is why I chose to leave my home and pursue higher education in Germany. I'm an avid reader and rock music fan. I hope you that you find something of value on my website. If you have any questions, send me an email over my website's contact form.
